Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.4 06/33] platform/x86: dell-laptop: disable kbd backlight on Inspiron 10xx
Date:   Thu, 23 Jan 2020 20:16:41 -0500
Message-Id: <20200124011708.18232-6-sashal@kernel.org>
